        Body Corporate By-Laws: What Brisbane Unit Sellers Need to Know Before Listing
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        By-laws govern what buyers can actually do with your apartment or townhouse. Sellers who understand them before listing avoid awkward conversations mid-campaign and protect their sale price.
      </p>
